ting cuts to their legal aid budgets, such as Australia, Scotland, France, and the Netherlands.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aLAW / Civil Law.2bisacsh1 aNewbury, Alex, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z97831111966330 cprintz978144733545040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447335467423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447335467/original  a978-3-11-119663-3  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles